        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Copilot 現可免費用 ChatGPT o1，一個設定加強提升解答精確度</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/03/microsoft-copilot-integrates-gpt-o1/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-copilot-integrates-gpt-o1</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/03/microsoft-copilot-integrates-gpt-o1/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 06:35:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-o1]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Microsoft Copilot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1289641</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Microsoft 日前宣佈免費開放 OpenAI 的 GPT-o1 推理模型 「Think Deeper」 予所有 Copilot 用户。GPT-o1 模型可利用深層思考，透過逐步生成推理過程來提升答案精確度，減少錯誤與低品質內容。</p><p>GPT-o1 的「Think Deeper」功能讓 Copilot 能處理更複雜的問題。用户只需點擊 Copilot 內的「Think Deeper」按鈕，AI 便會從多個角度審視問題，並提供更全面的回應。由於此功能涉及深入推理，處理時間較長，回應可能需時 30 秒以上。Microsoft AI 總裁 Mustafa Suleyman 在 LinkedIn 表示：「所有 Copilot 用户均可免費使用 OpenAI 的世界級 GPT-o1 推理模型。」，鼓勵用户親身體驗其強大功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1289660 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020315738-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020315738-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020315738.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020312833-357x580.jpg" alt="" width="357" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020312833-357x580.jpg 357w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020312833.jpg 555w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 357px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/mustafa-suleyman_today-weve-made-think-deeper-free-and-available-activity-7290487808706715648-Hj3S">Mustafa Suleyman@LinkedIn</a></p><p>然而 Microsoft 宣佈免費提供 GPT-o1 之際，也引起部分用户關注。ElectroNet 英國總監 James Crouch 在貼文回應指，在得悉 Microsoft Copilot 免費提供 GPT-o1 後 24 小時內，便收到 Microsoft 365 家庭版，訂閲價格上調 31% 的通知，質疑 Microsoft 是否透過調整價格來間接轉嫁成本，以「一手加價、一手免費」的策略平衡開支。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1289645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020313432-694x229.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="229" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020313432-694x229.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025020313432.jpg 1102w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/mustafa-suleyman_today-weve-made-think-deeper-free-and-available-activity-7290487808706715648-Hj3S">Mustafa Suleyman@LinkedIn</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/news/603149/microsoft-openai-o1-model-copilot-think-deeper-free">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.theregister.com/2025/01/31/microsoft_open_ai_reasoning_copilot/">The Register</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
